main event: A UFO sighting was reported by a civilian youth over Utica, New York, on August 8, 1966.
interesting points: The sighting lasted approximately 30 seconds., The object was reported as round and white., The object was observed visually with no sound or discernible features., Multiple celebrations in the area were noted which could explain potential reflections., The final evaluation suggested it could have been an aircraft or a reflection from search lights.
